                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/4754: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-05-05T12:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 5, 1927—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>84. For Stimson: Your 122, May 4, 4 p.m. and 123, May 4, 7 p.m. have been
                    received and shown to the President. The Navy is transmitting necessary
                    instructions to Admiral Latimer.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
